byline.original: By ADAM W. KEPLER; Compiled by PATRICIA COHEN

snippet: The “Sunday Night Football” game between the Green Bay Packers and the Atlanta Falcons dominated the night en route to another Sunday ratings victory for NBC.
lead_paragraph: The “Sunday Night Football” game between the Green Bay Packers and the Atlanta Falcons dominated the night en route to another Sunday ratings victory for NBC.
